# Tauri
apps/desktop/src-tauri/target

# Local, user-specific caches inside any wipe board
**/.wipe/.cache/

# The built desktop UI is committed under crates/wipe-daemon/assets/ so it is
# embedded into the wipe binary across ALL distribution channels (crates.io,
# npm, prebuilt binaries). Rebuild + commit it with `scripts/embed-ui` whenever
# the desktop UI changes. (node_modules etc. are still ignored globally above.)

# Local sandbox: persistent mock projects for running the CLI / agents locally
tests/sandbox/

# The repo does not dogfood its own board; a stray root .wipe/ is never committed.
/.wipe/

# Working build log (per project convention)
/PLAN.md

